The paper proposes a novel approach for improving sequence-generation models using reinforcement learning. This topic falls under the intersection of several sub-fields in computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
